data.description: Own an oasis right next to Mt Rainier national park - a perfect spot for an Air B & B!  This property boasts a level and fully fenced lot on a quiet street within a few miles of the Longmire entrance to the park.  The house has a metal roof and siding for minimal maintenance, inside is a bright and open floorpan with LVP flooring and stainless steel appliances. Keep cool in the summer with either air conditioning or swim in one of the two community lakes located within the HOA.   There is a park with a playground (its being updated now) and a community center that residents can utilize.  Dues are a very reasonable $265 a year!  This property is surrounded by forested hills for hiking and camping and is a short walk to the Nisqually river.
